description:
► Subscribe to Vision Video for more faith-based movies and tv series: https://bit.ly/3LrbGIN

Having just killed Goliath, the Philistine champion, David is invited to the King’s Headquarters for celebration with the Royal Family and the army’s top-brass. Crown Prince Jonathan and David become best friends and David makes a fast track career in the King’s army. Some time later David gets to marry Michal, the King’s youngest daughter. There’s no stopping this shepherd boy from Bethlehem; the whole country knows him by now and loves him. However, one day King Saul quietly decides that he feels overshadowed by David’s fame and charisma. His hatred for David grows from resenting his son-in-law to an actual first attempt to kill him.  

Billy Angel tells the Biblical story like you've never heard it before.
fulltitle: The Storyteller | Episode 11 | David Rises to Fame
